  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>陆拾柒</span> <span>2025-12-13 08:00</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">广东</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0dea2b8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FicvmTEvIjJrcWHpJNicGy0YPxOMRX0L5Gt8HKQkofQ7hBa9ozBfGcHwZNofuoC8Dic7DyYYUVianCkTd6PHpAhAF7A%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>wenyan-mcp 是一个基于模型上下文协议 (MCP) 的开源服务器组件，旨在自动排版和发布 Markdown 格式的文章到微信公众号草稿箱。它支持多种内置主题和自动图片上传，提供本地和 Docker 部署选项</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100004047\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.12222222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"71\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=01a1e263&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FicvmTEvIjJrclXNmw98AfC4PbBLib2ibXDkXEU5dbGtqBibHGVR6LFK1UEG2C3DyTU8Tyx00icA1QFklWmiclO0FIrsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <div data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-attachment: scroll;background-clip: border-box;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-image: none;background-origin: padding-box;background-position-x: 0%;background-position-y: 0%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: auto;width: auto;font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';font-size: 16px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height: 1.5em;word-spacing: 0em;letter-spacing: 0em;word-break: break-word;overflow-wrap: break-word;text-align: left;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;bor