em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持列出和选择多种内置主题，实现与文颜相同的排版效果</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(1, 1, 1);font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">自动上传本地或网络图片，方便文章配图管理</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(1, 1, 1);font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">提供本地运行和 Docker 运行两种部署方式，适应不同环境需求</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(1, 1, 1);font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">与 MCP Client 集成简便，通过配置即可实现公众号助手功能</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;color: rgb(1, 1, 1);font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持在 Markdown 文件中通过 frontmatter 配置标题、封面等元信息，提高发布灵活性</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 10px;padding-right: 0px;display: block;color: rgb(0, 150, 136);margin-top: 0.2rem;margin-right: auto;margin-bottom: 0.2rem;margin-left: auto;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 150, 136);\"><span style=\"font-size: 22px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: left;font-weight: bold;display: block;\"><span leaf=\"\">basecamp/omarchy</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.58em;font-weight: normal;font-style: italic;color: graytext;display: block;text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/basecamp/omarchy\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/basecamp/omarchy</a></span></span